  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of CS-3150 in Japanese Hypertensive Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Multi-center Study to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of CS-3150 in Japanese Subjects With Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
