  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a randomized, placebo-controlled, double-blind, multi-center study to evaluate
      efficacy and safety of different doses of CS-3150 compared to placebo in Japanese
      hypertensive subjects. Primary endpoint is change from baseline in sitting systolic and
      diastolic blood pressure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
